<p>Winnipeg Wonders is a local retail business established in 1995, specializing in unique handmade crafts and artisanal goods sourced directly from Manitoba artisans. We have 15 dedicated employees and currently operate two physical stores in Winnipeg's bustling Exchange District and St. Boniface neighborhoods. Our products range from pottery and textiles to handcrafted jewelry and artwork. We aim to provide high-quality, unique products to residents of Winnipeg and surrounding areas.</p>
